sections.comments: ALL STUDENTS: This section of the course is online - distance education. Your instructor and course support staff will contact you by email prior to and during the course. Please ensure that you have a valid email account. You will need your Campus Wide Login (CWL) to login to your course at https://www.elearning.ubc.ca/ . Course materials must be ordered or picked up at the designated bookstore source. Note that Proctorio (online exam proctoring) is not available for this course.
